{"url":"https://www.query.jp/recruit/systems/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n\n<head>\n\t<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n\t<meta name=\"description\" content=\"株式会社クエリーの福利厚生・研修制度・社内データを公開し、働きやすさと成長機会を詳しく紹介します。\">\n\t<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"\">\n\t<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1, user-scalable=0\" />\n\t<meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\" />\n\n\t<title>働く環境を知る｜クエリー採用サイト</title>\n\n\t<meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"働く環境を知る｜クエリー採用サイト\" />\n\t<meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"web\" />\n\t<meta property=\"og:url\" content=\"https://www.query.jp/recruit/systems/\" />\n\t<meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"\" />\n\t<meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"クエリー採用サイト\" />\n\t<meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"株式会社クエリーの福利厚生・研修制度・社内データを公開し、働きやすさと成長機会を詳しく紹介します。\" />\n\n\t<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" href=\"/recruit/assets/img/common/apple-touch-icon.png\" />\n\t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/recruit/assets/img/common/android-icon.png\" />\n\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/recruit/assets/css/default.css\" />\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/recruit/assets/css/common.css\" />\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/recruit/assets/css/page.css\" />\n\n\t<!-- SimpleBar CSS -->\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simplebar@latest/dist/simplebar.css\">\n\n\t<!-- Slick -->\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/recruit/assets/css/slick-theme.css\">\n\t<link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/recruit/assets/css/slick.css\">\n\n\t<!-- Fonts -->\n\t<link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:ital,opsz,wght@0,14..32,100..900;1,14..32,100..900&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@100..900&family=Roboto:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&family=Zen+Kaku+Gothic+New:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n\n\t<!-- Jquery -->\n\t<script src=\"https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.7.1/jquery.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/waypoints/4.0.0/jquery.waypoints.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/simplebar@latest/dist/simplebar.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/recruit/assets/js/jquery.counterup.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/recruit/assets/js/jquery.inview.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/recruit/assets/js/slick.min.js\"></script>\n\t<script src=\"/recruit/assets/js/common.js\"></script>\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\t<header id=\"header\">\n\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"headerFlex\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"logo\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/common/headerLogo.svg\" alt=\"Query\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex inter\">Recruit</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headerInfo sp_hidden\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<nav>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/company/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">クエリーとは</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/people/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">働く仲間</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/systems/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">働く環境</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/jobs/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">募集要項</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.query.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">企業ページへ</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t</nav>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headButtons\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/entry/#newgrad\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">新卒 ENTRY</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/entry/#career\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">キャリア ENTRY</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"menuTrigger pc_hidden\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<span></span>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</header>\n\t<div id=\"dropMenu\">\n\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t<nav>\n\t\t\t\t<ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/company/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">クエリーとは</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/people/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">働く仲間</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/systems/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">働く環境</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/jobs/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">募集要項</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t\t<li>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://www.query.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">企業ページへ</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t</li>\n\t\t\t\t</ul>\n\t\t\t</nav>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"headButtons\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/entry/#newgrad\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">新卒 ENTRY</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"button\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"/recruit/entry/#career\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"tex\">キャリア ENTRY</span>\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n\n\t<main>\n\t\t<section id=\"systems\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"head\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h1>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>働く環境を知る</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>Our Culture</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t</h1>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"headTex\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<p>クエリーでは性別にとらわれない働きやすさを追求し、<br class=\"sp_hidden\">誰もが安心して挑戦できる環境を整えています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"headImage\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/ourVisual-sp.png\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/ourVisual.png\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section><!-- /#systems-->\n\n\t\t<section id=\"systemInfo\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"head\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>基本情報や福利厚生</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Work style</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"iconList\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box01\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/styleIcon01.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>社会保険完備</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>雇用保険、労災保険、健康保険、厚生年金などの各種社会保険に加入し、安心して働ける基盤を整えています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box02\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/styleIcon02.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>出産・育児・介護休暇制度</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>労働基準法に基づく産前産後休暇、育児休暇、介護休暇の取得を推進し、給付金の支給や特別有給も付与しています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box03\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/styleIcon03.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>出産お祝い金</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>社員または配偶者の出産時にお祝い金を支給し、双子などのケースにも対応。ライフイベントを金銭的にもサポートします。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box04\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/styleIcon04.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>健康診断・予防接種補助</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>年1回の定期健康診断を会社負担で実施し、オプション検査やインフルエンザ・風疹ワクチンの費用も全額補助します。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box05\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/styleIcon05.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>出社環境の整備手当</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>入社祝金・支度金・引越し補助を支給し、遠方からの引越しや一人暮らしスタートを金銭面でしっかりサポートします。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box06\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/styleIcon06.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>社食＆フリードリンク</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>オフィス内に置き社食とフリードリンクを常備し、リフレッシュしながら働ける環境を提供しています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"texList\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box01\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>完全週休二日 年間休日120日</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box02\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>有給休暇数 <br class=\"pc_hidden\">初年度10日/最高20日</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box03\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>通勤手当支給</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>※通勤費は実費、月額限度額30,000円</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box04\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>その他各種手当</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section><!-- /#systemInfo -->\n\n\t\t<section id=\"systemTraining\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"head\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>研修・学習制度</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Training & <br>Learning System</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"newFaceBox\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"boxHead\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>新入社員研修</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"scrollList\" data-simplebar>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/trainingImg01.png\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"addTex\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>※研修終了時点で一定の技量を満たしていないと判断した場合、職種変更させて頂く場合がございます。<br>※状況によりOJT研修（現場への配属）が早まることがあります。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"iconList\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box01\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/trainingIcon01.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>資格取得支援</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>クエリーではAWS認定やMicrosoft認定、応用情報技術者試験など、多彩な資格取得をバックアップし、一人ひとりのキャリアアップを後押しします。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box02\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"icon\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/trainingIcon02.svg\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"conts\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>社内勉強会開催</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>定期的に社内勉強会を実施し、社員同士が知見を共有し合うことで、業務に直結する実践的なスキルを身に付ける場を提供しています。</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t</section><!-- /#systemTraining -->\n\n\t\t<section id=\"systemData\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"head\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>データで見るクエリー</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>Data</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t</h2>\n\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"dataFlex\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"box box01\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b>平均有給休暇 取得日数</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>（2024年度実績）</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"countUp\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"js-count\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<b class=\"count\">14.5</b>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<small>日</small>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<source media=\"(max-width: 768px)\" srcset=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/tadaImg01-sp.png\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img src=\"/recruit/assets/img/systems/tadaImg01.png\" alt=\"\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</picture>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t</div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=